Information We Collect
We collect several types of information in connection with your use of the App, including:
Personal Information: This includes information that can be used to identify you, including your name, email address, phone number, and any other information that you provide to us.
Usage Data: This includes information that is automatically generated by the App when you use it, such as your IP address, browser type, device type, mobile operating system, and other usage information.
Location Data: If you have enabled location services on your device and agreed to give us permission to access your device's location, we may collect and use your location data to provide you with localized content and services.
How We Use Your Information
We use the information that we collect from you to improve the App and to provide you with a better experience. Specifically, we may use your information to:
Provide you with access to the App and its features;
Remember your preferences and personalize your experience with the App;
Communicate with you about updates, news, and other information about the App;
Analyze and improve the App's performance and user experience;
Protect the security and integrity of the App and its users; and
Comply with applicable laws and regulations.
How We Protect Your Information
We take reasonable steps to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, use, or disclosure. For example, we use industry-standard encryption protocols to protect your data in transit and in storage. We also limit access to your personal information to employees and contractors who have a need to know in order to provide you with the services and features of the App.
We cannot guarantee the security of your data, and we cannot be held responsible for any unauthorized access, use, or disclosure of your personal information that is beyond our control.
Disclosure Of Your Information
We may disclose your personal information to third-party service providers who assist us in providing the App and its features. These service providers are contractually obligated to protect your information and use it only for the purpose of providing the services that we have requested.
We may also disclose your information if required to do so by law or in response to a legal request from law enforcement or other government authorities.
Changes to this Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to change this Privacy Policy at any time by posting a revised version on the App. Your continued use of the App after we have posted the revised Privacy Policy constitutes your agreement to the revised terms.
Contact Information
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or VANA's privacy practices, please contact us at hello@findyourVANA.com.